{"tid":1215050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔開會，我地仲有大把野要做！！！","createTime":"2019-06-13T05:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T06:29:30.000Z","uid":24590,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3a5eefabd59af226ae53bbb772d20e8f1e7b394c","tid":1215050,"uid":24590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:57:40.000Z","msg":"一）選票壓力<br />\n要比建制議員知佢地投贊成票有咩後果，需要文宣發放比各區選民，最好有埋地圖睇你係邊區選民，有街站更好。<br />\n如果有屋企人話比佢知！！著數可以照拎！！票一定唔可以投！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eac.hk/ch/distco/2019dc_elect_map.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eac.hk%2Fch%2Fdistco%2F2019dc_elect_map.htm&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=36456954\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eac.hk/ch/distco/2019dc_elect_map.htm</a> 地圖<br />\n地區直選：<strong><ins>港島、九龍東、九龍西、新界東、新界西！！！</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VRTt9WC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVRTt9WC.jpg&h=b7e0b688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n區議會投出黎的功能組別：<strong><ins>李慧琼、周浩鼎、劉國勳 </ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yovHuWC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyovHuWC.jpg&h=3eb98c65&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n19年的區議會選舉投票日定為今年11月24日！請各方面幫手！<br />\n<br />\n二）聯署<br />\n針對條例：<br />\n民陣「反送中 民意不可欺 為香港企硬」全球聯署（暫有65萬人簽署）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2I9PZ0l\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2I9PZ0l&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=2065f55d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2I9PZ0l</a><br />\n要求制裁香港《逃犯條例》修訂案負責人（4萬人簽署，差6萬人達標）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZilNG7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZilNG7&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=398bad93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZilNG7</a><br />\n制裁違反美國利益的香港官員（5,900人簽署，差9.4萬人達標）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ZgQ1JE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ZgQ1JE&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=19fbbb9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ZgQ1JE</a><br />\n要求美國反對香港修訂《逃犯條例》（11.5萬人簽署，已達標）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2VIWFLs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2VIWFLs&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=c0d14ae9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2VIWFLs</a><br />\n吊銷支持修訂《逃犯條例》中港官員簽證及美國國籍（已達標）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MGcgY8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MGcgY8&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=988e8ef7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MGcgY8</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">＊需要禁 email去comfirm</span></strong><br />\n韓國青瓦台聯署 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1213446\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1213446</a><br />\n<br />\n三）針對警察行為：<br />\n拒絕香港違反人權官員簽證入境（2,900人簽署，差9.72萬人達標）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2X9hZJS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2X9hZJS&d=NXUP4IJ4la%2FJDnFlXEjtWAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=97d675c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2X9hZJS</a><br />\n<strong><ins>[惡貫滿盈]黑警惡行整合 - 求支援- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1210640\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1210640</a></ins></strong><br />\n攻擊位<br />\n&gt;布袋彈鎮暴只可射下肢 根據15/01/2006的指引<br />\n&gt;阻住救護工作<br />\n&gt;不尊重記者探訪<br />\n&gt;未舉黑旗就射<br />\n請研究下以上事項可以sd去邊個單位/組織，其後再draft email。<br />\n<br />\n四）分散物資、處理垃圾<br />\n應該四周圍有d物資需要散去。請入物資/車隊group<br />\n另外十八區tg group一陣補上。<br />\n<br />\n五）和理非<br />\n&gt;銀行轉晒做美元/拎現金，保障你資產，順便做唔到money creation。<br />\n         ＊團結先有用<br />\n&gt;地鐵唔舒服 （注意：過份使用會造成市民反感）<br />\n&gt;唱聖詩<br />\n<br />\n六）極需要大量野<br />\n聯署整合 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1214756/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1214756/page/1</a><br />\n整合警察名單同相 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1213434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1213434/page/1</a><br />\n警察惡行 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1211515/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1211515/page/1</a> <br />\n[6.12] Reddit 文宣整合 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1208223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1208223</a><br />\n需要開放的地方同醫療服務中心整合！！<br />\n<br />\n翻譯支援：中英標題 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1211840\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1211840</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>大家有任何資訊請互通，但不要盲信，以免造成恐慌，如已有任何已開相關的telegram channel請留下。</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再講多次！我地無做過任何暴力行為！！係一路比警察暴力對待！！</span></span><br />\n***記得backup所有片同證據****"},{"pid":"dbfe75816a3ae5a224261386d4b5e61f2ac3249e","tid":1215050,"uid":24590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:13:00.000Z","msg":"錯圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地區直選：<strong><ins>港島、九龍東、九龍西、新界東、新界西！！！</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e5DNGFz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe5DNGFz.jpg&h=1cb35eca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2c68067941bfe01f9c95f4967759f1aac478850","tid":1215050,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:17:02.000Z","msg":"推 呢啲大家都可以做"},{"pid":"cc74a5d59665bed520a133536ab6449f10577adf","tid":1215050,"uid":126054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1feeb77755b26db497a6f5e23c497d44b964eb","tid":1215050,"uid":224323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"唔好講選舉。<br />\n<br />\n選舉只有你人性醜惡的黑歷史，退一步，淨係講投票大包圍支持反對棄權缺席全包宴，動議本人缺席，太多嘢講。<br />\n<br />\n經過褫奪議席的荒唐，再